#: /root/joao/TTMediaBot/bot/app_vars.py:11
msgid ""
"Hello! I am João Almeida. This is my fork of TTMediaBot for TeamTalk 5.\n"
"This repository focuses on stability and support for YouTube Music.\n"
"Repository: https://github.com/JoaoDEVWHADS/TTMediaBot\n"
"Original Authors: Amir Gumerov, Vladislav Kopylov, Beqa Gozalishvili, "
"Kirill Belousov.\n"
msgstr ""
"مرحباً! أنا João Almeida. هذا هو fork الخاص بي من TTMediaBot لـ TeamTalk "
"5.\n"
"يركز هذا المستودع على الاستقرار ودعم YouTube Music.\n"
"المستودع: https://github.com/JoaoDEVWHADS/TTMediaBot\n"
"المؤلفون الأصليون: Amir Gumerov, Vladislav Kopylov, Beqa Gozalishvili, "
"Kirill Belousov.\n"

